data.description: Do you love the peace and quiet of country life? This engaging corner property on 1.66 acres in Loxahatchee has that exact appeal. Easy to get to just west on Northlake. Relax inside or outside;split bedroom floor plan. The screened in pool is similar to one that you would find at a boutique hotel...long and lengthy for that morning swim. If you love to entertain and cook you have a bright open kitchen with granite counter tops, soft close drawers and stainless steel appliances. The bathrooms look like something from Pinterest with quartz counter, glass mosaic accent wall and a custom glass shower enclosure with a rain drop shower head and high speed jets...what a great thing to come home to at the end of your day. Sprinkler system newer. Close to equestrian, golf and Publix. Appt only.
